      "message": "As it\u0027s a package that contains more than one function, it does multiple things I suppose -- It contains Lookup, which is used to lookup the relevant project config group ID; it also contains a function used to update the state. And will the GobMap datastore model be here too?\n\nWDYT about something like: \"Package gobmap contains logic related to the mapping between GoB (Git/Gerrit-on-Borg) {host, repo, ref} combinations and project config groups.\n\nA mapping is stored in datastore and updated when project configs are updated. It is used to determine which project config group to use for a given Gerrit CL.\"",
